  "remarks": "As of mid-2007, he provided support to the Taliban in the form of weapons\nand money. Believed to be in the Gulf region. Belongs to Taraki tribe. Review pursuant\nto Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 23 Jul. 2010. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
